@startuml LangChain_TS_学习时序图

skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam sequenceArrowThickness 2

title LangChain TypeScript 学习阶段时序图

actor "学习者" as learner
participant "阶段1\n基础" as p1
participant "阶段2\nRAG/Memory" as p2
participant "阶段3\nLangGraph" as p3
participant "阶段4\n生产化" as p4
participant "实战项目" as project

== Week 1-2: 基础入门 ==

learner -> p1: 1. 环境配置\nNode.js + TypeScript
activate p1
p1 --> learner: 项目模板
learner -> p1: 2. 学习 Model I/O\nChatOpenAI 调用
p1 --> learner: API 集成能力
learner -> p1: 3. 掌握 LCEL\n管道语法 |
p1 --> learner: 链式组合思维
deactivate p1

== Week 3-4: 核心组件 ==

learner -> p2: 4. Memory 系统\nBuffer/Window/Summary
activate p2
p2 --> learner: 上下文管理能力
learner -> p2: 5. RAG 流程\nLoad → Split → Embed → Store
p2 --> learner: 向量检索能力
learner -> p2: 6. Agents 基础\nTools + ReAct
p2 --> learner: 自主决策能力
deactivate p2

== Week 5-6: LangGraph ==

learner -> p3: 7. StateGraph 构建\nNodes + Edges
activate p3
p3 --> learner: 状态管理思维
learner -> p3: 8. 持久化配置\nCheckpointer
p3 --> learner: 会话记忆能力
learner -> p3: 9. 人机协同\ninterrupt()
p3 --> learner: 安全控制机制
deactivate p3

== Week 7-8: 生产化 ==

learner -> p4: 10. 流式处理\nstreamEvents
activate p4
p4 --> learner: 实时响应能力
learner -> p4: 11. 可观测性\nLangSmith
p4 --> learner: 全链路追踪
deactivate p4

== 毕业项目 ==

learner -> project: 多Agent协作系统\n研究+写作+审核
activate project
project --> learner: 完整工程能力
deactivate project

@enduml